<h2>🔧 What You'll Learn</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Human activity detection using Ultralytics (YOLO)</li>
  <li>Real-time behavior monitoring</li>
  <li>Video stream processing and analysis</li>
  <li>AI-powered surveillance and insights</li>
</ul>

